# line-string-close-brace

## Input

```
a }not-close
b } with space

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..28
  ENTRY@0..13
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..12
      STRING@2..12 "}not-close"
    NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
  ENTRY@13..28
    WORD_KEY@13..14
      WORD@13..14 "b"
    SPACE@14..15 " "
    LINE_STRING@15..27
      STRING@15..27 "} with space"
    NEWLINE@27..28 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@2..12 "}not-close",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@13..14 "b",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@15..27 "} with space",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

